    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144130/extras/a2ecc9d4c2be9bbfe79bea3de45c569a.avif?t=1724158860\" width=596 height=168 /></span><br><br><strong>Loop Frogs</strong> is a pixelated <i>2D puzzle platformer</i> with a temporal component. Take control of two lovable frogs and master the <strong>Time Loop</strong> to save the day. Set a repeating loop of actions with one frog while the other discovers the route to advance. Can you beat over 30 levels of treacherous platforming and timing puzzles?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144130/extras/666132fd4c2ead316d148503c68ccf72.avif?t=1724158860\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144130/extras/4a9f51d81fce371ad607c9f370520d49.poster.avif?t=1724158860\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144130/extras/4a9f51d81fce371ad607c9f370520d49.webm?t=1724158860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144130/extras/4a9f51d81fce371ad607c9f370520d49.mp4?t=1724158860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144130/extras/896169911afe048af2f133c49afef57f.avif?t=1724158860\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144130/extras/c488dada58f4ef946f33c9d7c8a0c875.poster.avif?t=1724158860\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_